  "title": "Cashier (Retail, Islandwide)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Handle sales using the POS system and accept various payment methods.</li>\n  <li>Provide friendly assistance and share information on promotions or offers.</li>\n  <li>Manage cash accurately, including opening and closing duties.</li>\n  <li>Keep the counter clean, organized, and help with general store tasks when needed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>GCE N Level</li>\n  <li>At least 1 year of <strong>cashier</strong> experience in <strong>retail</strong>, including <strong>handling cash and assisting customers</strong></li>\n  <li>Basic knowledge of POS systems and payment methods.</li>\n  <li>Strong attention to detail and commitment to maintaining transaction accuracy.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in <strong>MS Word</strong> to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R21100996</p>",
